This paper discusses time synchronization in wireless sensor networks, which is a topic related to networked systems and communication (cs.NI). The paper also discusses hierarchical extensions and performance analysis, which are topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of message exchanges and simulations, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG).
